    <Text>
        I watched as he juggled kittens in a circular motion.
    </Text>
    <List>
      <ListItem>Morally wrong. Most people would consider this wrong because newborn kittens are fragile and could be harmed when tossed around.</ListItem>
    </List>
    <Text>
        I let him juggle the various balls and the newborn kittens watched the circular motion.
    </Text>
    <List>
	    <ListItem>
		    Not morally wrong. This isn't harming anyone and might be interesting to the kittens.</ListItem>
    </List>
